						"text": "Here's a simple n8n workflow with a Manual Trigger and a Set node:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Artifact Card Test Workflow\",\n  \"nodes\": [\n    {\n      \"parameters\": {},\n      \"id\": \"1\",\n      \"name\": \"Manual Trigger\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger\",\n      \"typeVersion\": 1,\n      \"position\": [240, 300]\n    },\n    {\n      \"parameters\": {\n        \"assignments\": {\n          \"assignments\": [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"field1\",\n              \"name\": \"message\",\n              \"value\": \"Hello from artifact card test!\",\n              \"type\": \"string\"\n            }\n          ]\n        }\n      },\n      \"id\": \"2\",\n      \"name\": \"artifact card test\",\n      \"type\": \"n8n-nodes-base.set\",\n      \"typeVersion\": 3.4,\n      \"position\": [460, 300]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"connections\": {\n    \"Manual Trigger\": {\n      \"main\": [\n        [\n          {\n            \"node\": \"artifact card test\",\n            \"type\": \"main\",\n            \"index\": 0\n          }\n        ]\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"active\": false,\n  \"settings\": {\n    \"executionOrder\": \"v1\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### What this workflow does:\n- **Manual Trigger** — Starts the workflow when you click *\"Execute Workflow\"*\n- **artifact card test** (Set node) — Sets a single field `message` with the value `\"Hello from artifact card test!\"`\n\n### To use it:\n1. Copy the JSON above\n2. In n8n, go to **Workflows → Import from JSON**\n3. Paste and save\n4. Click **Execute Workflow** to run it\n\nYou can add more fields in the Set node or connect additional nodes after it as needed!"
